                                                  bǝrhān</title>
                       <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                         <locus target="#162r" facs="162"> f. 162r, col. 2</locus>
                         Scribal note:
                       <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተፈጸመ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ዳዊት፡ በዘመነ፡ ማርቆስ፡ በወርኃ፡ ፆም፡ በብዙኅ፡ ምንዳቤ፡ በ፳፩፡ ሌሊት፡ በ፲ወ፬፡ መዓልት።</foreign>
                       “This Psalter was finished during the year of Mark, the Evangelist, in the fasting season with much suffering, on the twenty-first night, fourteenth day"
                       </colophon>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
